<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[DONGHYUK's dev]]></title><description><![CDATA[A starter blog demonstrating what Gatsby can do.]]></description><link>https://gatsby-starter-blog-demo.netlify.com</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2019 05:58:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[CRA에 Babel Plugin 추가하기]]></title><description><![CDATA[CRA 설치 CRA 프로젝트 만들기 react-app-rewired, customize-cra 설치 test 폴더 안에서 @babel/plugin-proposal-optional-chaining 설치 config-overrides.js…]]></description><link>https://gatsby-starter-blog-demo.netlify.com/how-to-add-babel-plugin-to-cra/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://gatsby-starter-blog-demo.netlify.com/how-to-add-babel-plugin-to-cra/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h3&gt;CRA 설치&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; -g create-react-app&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;CRA 프로젝트 만들기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;create-react-app &lt;span class=&quot;token builtin class-name&quot;&gt;test&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token builtin class-name&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token builtin class-name&quot;&gt;test&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;react-app-rewired, customize-cra 설치&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;test&lt;/strong&gt; 폴더 안에서&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; --save-dev react-app-rewired customize-cra&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;@babel/plugin-proposal-optional-chaining 설치&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; --save-dev @babel/plugin-proposal-optional-chaining&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;config-overrides.js 파일 생성&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; useBabelRc&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; override &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;customize-cra&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
module&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;exports &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;override&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;useBabelRc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;.babelrc.js 파일 생성&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;module&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;exports &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  plugins&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;@babel/plugin-proposal-optional-chaining&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;package.json 수정&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;scripts&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;start&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;react-app-rewired start&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;build&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;react-app-rewired build&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  ...
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;VS Code 경고 제거&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;.vscode/settings.json&lt;/code&gt; 파일 생성 후&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;javascript.validate.enable&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token boolean&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Gatsby, Github page로 블로그 만들기]]></title><description><![CDATA[Nodes.js 설치 Node.js LTS 다운로드 gatsby-cli 설치 터미널 환경에서 Gatsby 프로젝트 만들기 gatsby new [원하는 블로그 이름] [원하는 스타터 패키지(테마)] 로컬 개발 환경 실행하기 브라우저에서 http…]]></description><link>https://gatsby-starter-blog-demo.netlify.com/how-to-make-a-blog-using-gatsby/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://gatsby-starter-blog-demo.netlify.com/how-to-make-a-blog-using-gatsby/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h3&gt;Nodes.js 설치&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nodejs.org/ko/&quot;&gt;Node.js&lt;/a&gt; LTS 다운로드&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;gatsby-cli 설치&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;터미널&lt;/strong&gt; 환경에서&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; -g gatsby-cli&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Gatsby 프로젝트 만들기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;gatsby new [[원하는 블로그 이름]] [[원하는 스타터 패키지(테마)]]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;ex&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; gatsby new my_blog https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-blog&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;로컬 개발 환경 실행하기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token builtin class-name&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;블로그 이름&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; gatsby develop&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;브라우저에서 &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8000&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8000&lt;/a&gt; 접속 후&lt;br&gt;
자신의 입맛대로 블로그를 꾸며보자. (스타터 패키지에 따라 코드 및 테마가 다름)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;일단 github.io repo를 만들자.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com&quot;&gt;https://github.com&lt;/a&gt; 접속 및 로그인&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;오른쪽 상단 +버튼 클릭, New Repository&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repository name에 [[사용자_이름]].github.io 입력&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Public으로 만든다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Github remote 연결&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; remote origin &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt; https://github.com/&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;사용자 이름&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;/&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;사용자 이름&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;.github.io.git&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Github page로 배포하기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;gh-pages 모듈 설치&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; --save-dev gh-pages&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;package.json에 배포 스크립트 작성&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;scripts&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;&quot;deploy&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;gatsby build &amp;amp;&amp;amp; gh-pages -d public -b master&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;개발, 배포 브랜치 나누기 및 배포하기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;본인&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;master&lt;/code&gt;(배포), &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;dev&lt;/code&gt;(개발, 본인이 원하는 이름 아무 거나 하셔도 됩니다 ,, 제 지인은 source로 하더라구요.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;dev에서 개발하고 master에 merge한 뒤,&lt;br&gt;
master에서 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;npm run deploy&lt;/code&gt; 명령어를 통해 배포하고 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;사용하기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;https://[[사용자 이름]].github.io&lt;/code&gt;로 접속&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item></channel></rss>